# Well-formed structural fixture (step 1)

<!-- k4k:owner=user begin id=goal -->
## Goal
A toy CLI that echoes its argv.
<!-- k4k:owner=user end -->

<!-- k4k:owner=user begin id=inputs-outputs -->
## Inputs and outputs
- argv: any positional args
- stdin: ignored
- stdout: argv joined by spaces, plus newline
- stderr: empty
- exit codes: 0 on success
<!-- k4k:owner=user end -->

<!-- k4k:owner=user begin id=errors -->
## Error taxonomy
N/A: no error paths in v0
<!-- k4k:owner=user end -->

